# Bug: Currency Conversion Not Applied Correctly

## Module
Financial Reports / Transactions

## Platforms
- Android
- iOS

## Description
Currency conversion is not functioning correctly. Only the currency symbol changes, while the actual transaction values remain unchanged.

## Steps to Reproduce
1. Navigate to financial data or reports  
2. Change currency  
3. Observe updated values  

## Expected Result
- Currency values should be recalculated based on the conversion rate  
- Both symbol and value should update  

## Actual Result
- Only the currency symbol changes  
- Values remain the same  

## Severity
High

## Priority
High

## Impact
- Displays incorrect financial data  
- Leads to serious user misinterpretation  
- Affects app credibility  

## Notes
Likely a missing conversion logic or API integration issue
